      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i know my levels usually spike after hard cardio because of the cortisol or whatever. i'm just really scared of staying high for too long. if i just do a small correction dose like 2 units, won't that be safer than just sitting here feeling like this? it's better to be proactive right?",
